An easy way to ensure first / second order just switch these lines to:

    CompletableFuture&lt;Void&gt; firstFuture = getFuture(firstSet);
    firstFuture.join();

    CompletableFuture&lt;Void&gt; secondFuture = getFuture(secondSet);
    secondFuture.join();

